PHINEAS AND FERB - "Flop Starz" There is a singing contest at the Googleplex Mall and Candace has to enter. Of course, Phineas and Ferb beat her to it and become one-hit wonders. To make matters worse, Candace is horrified to have to sing with them on stage. Meanwhile, Perry the Platypus foils Dr. Doofenshmirtz's evil plan to have a giant robot take over the city, on "Phineas and Ferb," airing FRIDAY, FEBRUARY 1 (8 p.m., ET) on Disney Channel.
